message.text:
𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐛𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝐡𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐛𝐢𝐠𝐠𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐒𝐌𝐈𝐋𝐄𝐒! 🎭

The ITHM Student Council carries smiles filled with gratitude and joy as we are honored to be awarded  “𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐰’𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐨𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐁𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐏𝐨𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫” in 𝐋𝐚𝐤𝐛𝐚𝐲 𝐏𝐢𝐲𝐮 𝐀𝐰𝐚𝐫𝐝𝐬! 🏆

This recognition is not just a win—it’s a tribute to Bacolod City and its MassKara Festival, a reflection of the smiles, passion, and vibrant community spirit that shine through ITHM’s mission.

Indeed, every smile wins! As we also got awarded as the “𝐖𝐢𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐇𝐚𝐬𝐡𝐭𝐚𝐠” with the #𝐁𝐢𝐝𝐚𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐒𝐚𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌. 🎉

Thank you to everyone who believed with smiles and voted with their hearts. 🩷💛

This is just one of the festivals ITHM brings that never fades—because here at ITHM, we are empowered through smiles. ✨

PubMat by: Akira Pagarigan
Caption by: Antonette Zaballero

message.text:
𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐛𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝐡𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐛𝐢𝐠𝐠𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐒𝐌𝐈𝐋𝐄𝐒! 🎭

The ITHM Student Council carries smiles filled with gratitude and joy as we are honored to be awarded  “𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐰’𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐨𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐁𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐏𝐨𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫” in 𝐋𝐚𝐤𝐛𝐚𝐲 𝐏𝐢𝐲𝐮 𝐀𝐰𝐚𝐫𝐝𝐬! 🏆

This recognition is not just a win—it’s a tribute to Bacolod City and its MassKara Festival, a reflection of the smiles, passion, and vibrant community spirit that shine through ITHM’s mission.

Indeed, every smile wins! As we also got awarded as the “𝐖𝐢𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐇𝐚𝐬𝐡𝐭𝐚𝐠” with the #𝐁𝐢𝐝𝐚𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐒𝐚𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌. 🎉

Thank you to everyone who believed with smiles and voted with their hearts. 🩷💛

This is just one of the festivals ITHM brings that never fades—because here at ITHM, we are empowered through smiles. ✨

PubMat by: Akira Pagarigan
Caption by: Antonette Zaballero

message.text:
𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌 𝐛𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝐡𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐛𝐢𝐠𝐠𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐒𝐌𝐈𝐋𝐄𝐒! 🎭

The ITHM Student Council carries smiles filled with gratitude and joy as we are honored to be awarded  “𝐓𝐚𝐦𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐰’𝐬 𝐂𝐡𝐨𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐁𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐏𝐨𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐫” in 𝐋𝐚𝐤𝐛𝐚𝐲 𝐏𝐢𝐲𝐮 𝐀𝐰𝐚𝐫𝐝𝐬! 🏆

This recognition is not just a win—it’s a tribute to Bacolod City and its MassKara Festival, a reflection of the smiles, passion, and vibrant community spirit that shine through ITHM’s mission.

Indeed, every smile wins! As we also got awarded as the “𝐖𝐢𝐭𝐭𝐢𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐇𝐚𝐬𝐡𝐭𝐚𝐠” with the #𝐁𝐢𝐝𝐚𝐒𝐦𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐒𝐚𝐈𝐓𝐇𝐌. 🎉

Thank you to everyone who believed with smiles and voted with their hearts. 🩷💛

This is just one of the festivals ITHM brings that never fades—because here at ITHM, we are empowered through smiles. ✨

PubMat by: Akira Pagarigan
Caption by: Antonette Zaballero

message.text:
𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐯𝐞𝐥 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐈𝐦𝐩𝐚𝐜𝐭: 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐋𝐢𝐠𝐡𝐭𝐬 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐖𝐚𝐲! ✈️🌏

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms! 

🗓️: 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟐, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓
🕰️: 𝟏:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 - 𝟒:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 
📍: 𝐒𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟏𝟎𝟐 - 𝟏𝟎𝟒

𝐑𝐞𝐠𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐋𝐢𝐧𝐤:

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms!

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms!

𝐖𝐨𝐫𝐥𝐝 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 presents 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐢𝐧 𝐀𝐜𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧, an exciting event centered on the theme “𝐄𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐰𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐕𝐨𝐥𝐮𝐧𝐭𝐞𝐞𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐚 𝐓𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐬𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐯𝐞 𝐓𝐨𝐮𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐦 𝐅𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞.” This event highlights how volunteer efforts can create meaningful change in communities and travel experiences worldwide.

Be part of the movement that combines passion for travel with a commitment to giving back. This is your chance to learn, connect, and take action for responsible tourism that uplifts lives and preserves cultures.

Register now and step into a journey where your time and skills make a lasting difference, PATAms! 

🗓️: 𝐒𝐞𝐩𝐭𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫 𝟐𝟐, 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓
🕰️: 𝟏:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 - 𝟒:𝟑𝟎 𝐩𝐦 
📍: 𝐒𝐜𝐢𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐁𝐮𝐢𝐥𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝟏𝟎𝟐 - 𝟏𝟎𝟒
